<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
        <main>
            <section class="page-header">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1>Work With Us</h1>
                    <p>Join our dedicated team and shape the future of education in rural India.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="content-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row" style="display: flex; gap: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                        <div style="flex: 2; min-width: 300px;">
                            <h2>Build a Rewarding Career with Impact</h2>
                            <p>At Nageshwaram Foundation Trust, we believe that our greatest asset is our people. We are
                                a growing organization committed to making a tangible difference in the lives of
                                students and communities. If you are passionate about education, driven by a desire to
                                serve, and eager to work in a dynamic and supportive environment, we invite you to
                                explore career opportunities with us.</p>
                            <p>We offer a collaborative culture where your contributions are valued, and your
                                professional growth is encouraged. Whether you are an experienced educator, an
                                administrative professional, or a support staff member, your skills can help us further
                                our mission.</p>

                            <h2 style="margin-top: 40px;">What We Look For</h2>
                            <ul style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
                                <li><strong>Passion for Education:</strong> A genuine commitment to fostering learning
                                    and holistic development.</li>
                                <li><strong>Dedication:</strong> A strong work ethic and a desire to make a positive
                                    impact.</li>
                                <li><strong>Team Player:</strong> Ability to collaborate effectively with colleagues,
                                    students, and parents.</li>
                                <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> Openness to new ideas and modern pedagogical
                                    approaches.</li>
                                <li><strong>Integrity:</strong> Adherence to high ethical standards and professional
                                    conduct.</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h2>Current Openings</h2>
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 15px;">We frequently have openings in various roles, including:</p>
                            <ul style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
                                <li>Teaching positions (various subjects and levels) at N.R.K. Public School</li>
                                <li>Administrative staff</li>
                                <li>Counselors</li>
                                <li>Support staff (librarians, lab assistants, etc.)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px;">
                            <div
                                style="background: var(--bg-cream); padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-gold);">
                                <h3>Apply Now</h3>
                                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">We are always keen to hear from talented individuals who
                                    share our vision.</p>
                                <a href="/contact" class="cta-button primary"
                                    style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">Send Your Resume</a>
                                <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9rem; text-align: center; color: #666;">or
                                    email us at <br><strong>careers@nageshwaram.org</strong></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>